# Adds some styling to comments

doc-emphazise when comment comment-line comment-block
	\*.*$

doc-highlight when comment comment-line comment-block
	:.*$

doc-warning when comment comment-line comment-block
	\?.*$

doc-todo when comment comment-line comment-block
	\bTODO\b.*$

doc-error when comment comment-line comment-block
	!.*$
